                    <span>This is a must have video! Becky Nee covers everything from the need for adoption to the paperwork, packing, traveling to China and bonding with baby. My husband and I took tons of notes and learned many new things through this informative video. In fact we are going to show it to our parents so they can better understand their grandaughter and where she came from. We feel we are much better prepared for our adoption trip next month. Also, it was touching to see her personal story and the moment she received her new daughter. I highly recommend!!!!</span>
                  
                    <div class="CustomerReviewSummary">Adoption from China - A Survival Guide</div>
                    <div>
                      <span class="ItemCaption">Rating: </span>
                      <span>5</span>
                      <span class="ItemCaption">Helpful: </span>
